      "message": "fTransform is the matrix var (either as a matrix or as a vector). It exists in either the VS (implicit) or FS (explicit) in all cases except NV_PR with non-explicit coords. There is no VS with NV_PR and instead you use a GL API to specify a matrix and it produces a varying (available as fVaryingPoint) in the FS.",
